360
00:22:45,772 --> 00:22:47,169
Mr. Liang, were your previous works

361
00:22:47,170 --> 00:22:48,648
in the competitions
actual original works?

362
00:22:49,013 --> 00:22:50,653
- Mr. Liang.
- Mr. Liang.

363
00:24:10,052 --> 00:24:11,213
