462
00:31:38,536 --> 00:31:39,064
What's wrong?

463
00:31:39,532 --> 00:31:41,372
You can't do it
when it's Liang Daiwen, huh?

464
00:31:44,413 --> 00:31:44,893
Ms. Zhang,

465
00:31:46,413 --> 00:31:47,532
