500
00:35:01,333 --> 00:35:02,013
Gu Yi.

501
00:35:04,453 --> 00:35:05,172
Don't do this.

502
00:35:10,373 --> 00:35:11,092
Liang Daiwen,

503
00:35:12,493 --> 00:35:13,973
